Commentary Text: Jadeja to Maxwell, out Lbw!! Back-to-back wickets for GL. Once more Maxwell has thrown away a start. He did that against MI as well and he's team suffered a big loss. Commentary Text: Shubham Agarwal to Amla, out Caught&Bowled!! Maiden IPL wicket for Shubham Agarwal. It's the big one. A well-set Amla departs soon after the strategic break. I guess it should be renamed to wicket-taking-break. Second time today that GL have got a wicket after the time-out. Flatter and on the stumps, Amla makes room and slaps it straight back, it was traveling quickly and Agarwal did well to bend down and pouch that. Made it look easy did the youngster. Commentary Text: Sandeep Sharma to Brendon McCullum, out Lbw!! Sandeep has the early wicket. That was dead in front. One of the easiest decisions Erasmus would have made.
